data.description: Available NOW! Don't miss this 5 Bed/3 Bath/ 3 Car Ranch style home situated in Bennington's Newport Vista neighborhood. Boasting over 3100 finished sq ft of living space this split bedroom ranch plan is on flat lot backing to trees & an acreage lot for the next level of privacy. When you enter the home you will notice the open & inviting modern farmhouse feel featuring shiplap walls, shaker cabinets, farmhouse sink, & black light fixtures.  The fireplace wall in the great room makes a  statement w/ a linear fireplace, shiplap, & built-in cabinets. The kitchen features modern high end style & a huge walk-in pantry w/ coffee bar, quartz countertops, custom cabinets with custom hood & birch shelving, & stylish hard wood floors. The primary suite is privately tucked away & adjoins the laundry room. Downstairs you will enjoy the fully finished basement complete w/ large rec room w/  fireplace, wet bar & island seating, 2 bedrooms, both w/ walk-in closets, 3/4 bathroom, & ample storage.
